</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-28_ pf-text-1"><strong>Legislative impact</strong> - DEFRA’s policies affect a wide range of industries, from agriculture to manufacturing, influencing over £100 billion of the UK economy annually.





