</h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-92_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">DEFRA's environmental policies are critical in addressing climate change and protecting natural resources. By setting strict emissions targets and promoting renewable energy, DEFRA ensures that businesses operate in an environmentally sustainable manner. Companies are encouraged to reduce their carbon footprint and invest in green technologies.






































